ActNuclear Safety and Control Act
PrecisRe-appointment of RUMINA VELSHI of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time permanent member of the Canadian Nuclear Safety Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on December 31, 2023; and her designation as President of the Canadian Nuclear Safety Commission effective August 22, 2023.
